{"tid":2222382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「懲教黑幕」背後有勢力人士撐腰 販賣探監用品圖利 懲教署未有執法","createTime":"2020-09-29T05:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T05:19:09.000Z","uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b21c18c3551069a73de8bc7377c7b95b7d17be9d","tid":2222382,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9Hgc4-odvzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9Hgc4-odvzU&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=48aabe88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9Hgc4-odvzU</a> <br />\n<br />\n監獄搶錢家族 霸佔訪客處賣探監用品圖利 活躍兩年月賺10萬<br />\n<br />\n荔枝角收押所的訪客登記處，本是讓在囚人士的親友辦理探監手續的場所，可是，有讀者向我們報料指，每天都有一個家庭式集團在這裏販賣探監物品，更離譜的是，他們霸佔了多個原本供探監人士擺放私人物品的儲物櫃作存貨之用；不過，在場的保安人員卻一直未有阻止他們的行為。除了賣探監物品，這一家人也提供代客探監的服務，亦染指赤柱監獄的相關生意。消息指，這個監獄搶錢家族每月賺取的利潤超過十萬，相當可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/skipped-hk/20200904/S7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fskipped-hk%2F20200904%2FS7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=a5cc07bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fskipped-hk%2F20200904%2FS7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI%2F&h=bbe4f63c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/skipped-hk/20200904/S7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI/</a>"},{"pid":"1ba20eb35c705755a6c9a4fb1c03e13fc5ab4ca1","tid":2222382,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"在荔枝角收押所外專營探訪日用品的士多負責人，一早知道蓮姐的存在，直斥其<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>行為非法，並質疑她有甚麼人給她撐腰</strong></span></span>。由於這個監獄搶錢家族，在荔枝角收押所活躍兩年，但卻一直未被懲教職員干預，因此，引起很多人不滿。"},{"pid":"777c64b40ea75fadee22526cfdd906126acfad01","tid":2222382,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0568436aa5528471b3e447b076b9ad6b69c92ac1","tid":2222382,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n蓮姐主要售賣的貨品組合，是俗稱「五大」的五款零食，魷魚絲、沙爹肉片、薄餅、朱古力，及魚片花生，搭配<strong><span class=\"red\">16包香煙，售價$638</span></strong><strong><span class=\"red\">，比收押所外的士多便宜超過兩成，</span></strong>因此，生意非常多。"},{"pid":"e74d8cfdc46a7d1cb0b53e70cea2fbd538744894","tid":2222382,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94b089a20e49effc45682f5561d9ea1fb15d5a5","tid":2222382,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b129d2d074a7c8b3013f7e4d1b5dab6fd0f53098","tid":2222382,"uid":117286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0568436aa5528471b3e447b076b9ad6b69c92ac1","tid":2222382,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n蓮姐主要售賣的貨品組合，是俗稱「五大」的五款零食，魷魚絲、沙爹肉片、薄餅、朱古力，及魚片花生，搭配<strong><span class=\"red\">16包香煙，售價$638</span></strong><strong><span class=\"red\">，比收押所外的士多便宜超過兩成，</span></strong>因此，生意非常多。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"平貴就無得講嘅，自由選擇，但可以佔用懲教地方擺貨就係特權"},{"pid":"1c23621d0c79d5725a544cce97a3391f8db169e0","tid":2222382,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}